# 2025-06-13 10:36:53.835845
+Your venv doesn't have PowerShell in PATH. Either:
+
+1. Use full path: C:\Windows\System32\WindowsPowerShell\v1.0\powershell.exe -Command "pip install azure-ai-foundry azure-identity"
+
+2. Or use python directly: python -m pip install azure-ai-foundry azure-identity
+
+3. Or activate pwsh in the venv: /run $env:PATH += ";C:\Program Files\PowerShell\7"
+
+The packages need to be installed IN your virtual environment, not globally.

